                                            "music/Capital/STARLIGHT.mp3",
                                          "EndLoop",
                                          "IfChoice", "1", "", "Tutorial",
                                          "SwapLineIf", "IfTimeIs",
                                            "DayTrue", "Wading through the lake, you approach the central lake island where the fishing Slimes have gathered, the ever industrious Seafoam giving you a small wave before pointing you to a free rod, letting you pick up your equipment and find a spot to set up amid the Slimes and their buckets of caught fish.",
                                            "NightTrue","Wading through the lake, you approach the central lake island where a handful of hardcore fisher Slimes are still at it under the tutelage of the ever industrious Seafoam who gives you a small wave before pointing you to a free rod, letting you pick up your equipment and easily find a spot to set up, most of the Slimes having gone home for the evening along with their many buckets of caught fish, leaving you plenty of space.",
                                          "EndLoop",
                                          "JumpToScene", "FishingMenu"
                                    ]
                      },
                            {
                                "NameOfScene": "Tutorial",
                                "theScene": [
                                              "SetChoice", "1", "FishingTutDone",
                                              "DisplayCharacters",
                                                "1",
                                              "EndLoop",
                                              "Noticing that most of the fishing Slimes seem to have gathered on the island at the center of Sleim Vllge's lake, you curiously wade through the shallow water to join them, and are welcomed by a particularly industrious-looking one holding an aged-looking rod, the Slime Girl waving over to you with a smile.",
                                              "Speak", "???",
                                              "Hehe, very busy today, isn't it?",
                                                "ChangeImageLayer", "Expression", "1", "Excited",
                                              "Her line gets a slight tug, giving her a small start before she starts to reel it in while the other Slimes watch excitedly, the fisher Slime still idly chatting to you while she expertly brings up her catch.",
                                              "Speak", "Seafoam",
                                              "I'm Seafoam. You must be [ThePlayerName]. I'll teach you how to fish, too.",
                                              "ChangeImageLayer", "Expression", "1", "Smug",
                                              "She says with businesslike authority, then with a flourishing pull of her rod and a resounding splash, she takes out a large fish that she deftly catches in one hand to proudly show off to you and the other Slimes, the assembled apprentice fishers oooing and ahhing and clapping admiratively.",
                                              "Speak", "Seafoam, Fishing Master of Sleim Vllge",
                                              "For I am Seafoam, Fishing Master of Sleim Vllge.",
                                              "She takes a moment to strike a smug pose, then unhooks the fish and tosses it back into the lake waters casually, prompting the other Slimes to focus back on their bobbers with redoubled attention, determined to get a catch to rival Seafoam's, the 'Fishing Master of Sleim Vllge' nodding contently at their eagerness before turning back to you with a more easygoing smile.",
                                              "ChangeImageLayer", "Expression", "1", "Base",
                                              "Speak", "Seafoam",
                                              "But you can just call me Seafoam. Here, take a rod.",
                                              "You wonder what kind you should choose, but before you know it, some of the nearby Slimes usher you forward, push a fishing rod into your hands, and seat you next to Seafoam, sparing you any indecision and leaving you a bit dizzy as the expert fisher Slime takes on an inspired air to explain.",
                                              "ChangeImageLayer", "Expression", "1", "Smile",
                                              "Speak", "Seafoam",
                                              "Fishing is actually very easy, and relaxing... You just need to wait for the right moment, and visuzalize... visulaize... {i}picture{/i} the fish in your mind's eye, tugging it out of the water as soon as it bites your hook, like plucking a helpless blueberry! ... Just don't go swinging randomly or the line will break.",
                                              "ChangeImageLayer", "Expression", "1", "ItsFine",
                                              "You're... not sure exactly what she means, but she just giggles nonchalantly at your nonplussed expression, and pats your shoulder reassuringly.",
                                              "Speak", "Seafoam",
                                              "I know it's kinda abstract and all, but don't worry: just give it a try and you'll get the hang of it in no time.",
                                              "ChangeImageLayer", "Expression", "1", "Excited",
                                              "Speak", "Seafoam",
                                              "So go on now, try it out!",
                                              "DisplayCharacters",
                                              "EndLoop",
                                              "Taking her word for it, you attach some bait to your hook and throw it into the lake's waters. You watch it sink... Then you wait.",
                                              "FishingMiniGame",
                                                "AppearTimerRange", "200", "500",
                                                "FailTimerRange", "400", "600",
                                                "ReelsNeeded", "1",
                                                "FishingPassJump", "FishCatchTut",
                                                "FishingFailJump", "FishCatchFailTut",
                                              "EndLoop"
                                          ]
                            },
                                  {
                                      "NameOfScene": "FishCatchTut",
                                      "theScene": [
                                                      "DisplayCharacters",
                                                        "1",
                                                      "EndLoop",
                                                      "ChangeImageLayer", "Expression", "1", "Excited",
                                                      "GetEventAndChangeProgress", "SleimVllge", "150",
                                                      "With a resounding splash, you pull a flopping fish from the depths of the lake, making the Slimes around you ooo and ahhh.",
                                                      "Speak", "Fisher Slimes",
                                                      "It's a Laek Fesh!",
                                                      "You're... not sure that's its actual name, but don't want to deflate their enthusiasm as they happily take your flopping catch off of your hook to place it into a nearby bucket while Seafoam gives you a cheerful nod of approval.",
                                                      "Speak", "Seafoam",
                                                      "Good job! I told you it was easy. Laek Fesh is very common and honestly nothing special, though, so an adventurer like you wouldn't really have any use for it... But it's still worth 150 Eros to the Vllg!",
                                                      "ChangeImageLayer", "Expression", "1", "Base",
                                                      "Speak", "Seafoam",
                                                      "But not all fish will be so simple... Sometimes, you will need to tug many times in a row... Or they'll get away faster... It allll depends on the fish you hook! So stay vigilant!",
                                                      "ChangeImageLayer", "Expression", "1", "Excited",
                                                      "Speak", "Seafoam",
                                                      "Every fish you catch will help the others learn and get better at fishing, too, so it'll help bring value to the village... So whenever you're in the mood, don't hesitate to come have a go!",
                                                      "ChangeImageLayer", "Expression", "1", "Smile",
                                                      "Speak", "Seafoam",
                                                      "That should cover the basics, so you have fun now. I'll be here if you need help.",
                                                      "Seafoam gives you a parting pat, then goes on to help one of the Slimes who managed to tangle herself in her fishing line somehow, leaving you to your own fishy devices...",
                                                      "JumpToScene", "FishingMenu"
                                                ]
                                  },
                                  {
                                      "NameOfScene": "FishCatchFailTut",
                                      "theScene": [
                                                      "DisplayCharacters",
                                                        "1",
                                                      "EndLoop",
                                                      "Despite your efforts, you fumble and feel the wriggling weight at the end of your line drop, then swiftly splash away into the safety of the lake's depths, eliciting compassionate awwws and pats from the assembled Slime Girls, including Seafoam.",
                                                      "Speak", "Seafoam",
                                                      "Ah... that's not good. But try again! I'm sure you'll get it this time...",
                                                      "DisplayCharacters",
                                                      "EndLoop",
                                                      "FishingMiniGame",
                                                        "AppearTimerRange", "50", "200",
                                                        "FailTimerRange", "500", "700",
                                                        "ReelsNeeded", "1",
                                                        "FishingPassJump", "FishCatchTut",
                                                        "FishingFailJump", "FishCatchFailTut",
                                                      "EndLoop"
