                          {
                              "NameOfScene": "How many fish have I caught?",
                              "theScene": [
                                              "DisplayCharacters",
                                                "1",
                                              "EndLoop",
                                              "Seafoam perks up cheerfully at your inquiry, and looks from her rod to you, as if the aged fishing implement somehow held the answer.",
                                              "ChangeImageLayer", "Expression", "1", "Excited",
                                              "Speak", "Seafoam",
                                              "You've caught [ProgressDisplay] fish so far!",
                                              "Speak", "Seafoam",
                                              "SwapLineIf", "Progress",
                                                "500",  "|f|ChangeImageLayer|/|Expression|/|1|/|Shy|n|Ah... Maybe I set you down the road to total fishing addiction... |f|ChangeImageLayer|/|Expression|/|1|/|Excited|n|Well, as long as you're having fun, it's fine... Just remember to take breaks! Even I do.",
                                                "250",  "|f|ChangeImageLayer|/|Expression|/|1|/|ItsFine|n|Hmmm... That's a ton of fish... You're not doing it just to impress me, are you? Hehe, you already have with how passionate you are about fishing! The village greatly appreciates your help, too, and so do I.",
                                                "100",  "|f|ChangeImageLayer|/|Expression|/|1|/|Excited Blush|n|Eh? That's... a lot... Are you sure you don't have adventurer stuff you should be doing? ... |f|ChangeImageLayer|/|Expression|/|1|/|Happy|n|Well, thank you very much for all your help regardless! I hope you're having lots of fun.♪",
                                                "50",  "|f|ChangeImageLayer|/|Expression|/|1|/|Smile|n|Oh, you've actually caught quite a lot now, huh? You must really enjoy doing this... Or maybe you want to help the village that much? ... Well, either way, we all appreciate you helping.",
                                                "25",  "|f|ChangeImageLayer|/|Expression|/|1|/|Happy|n|You're doing great! [ThePlayerName], the Greatest Novice Fisher...♪ |f|ChangeImageLayer|/|Expression|/|1|/|Smug|n|Let's see if you can catch at least 50! Then I'll stop calling you a novice, hehe.♪",
                                                "10",  "|f|ChangeImageLayer|/|Expression|/|1|/|Smug|n|That's enough to fill a few of the small buckets, huh? Most of the slimes around here can manage this much, but I know that's not the limits to your potential, novice... |f|ChangeImageLayer|/|Expression|/|1|/|Happy|n|So go ahead and make me proud!",
                                                "5",  "|f|ChangeImageLayer|/|Expression|/|1|/|Smile|n|Hmm... I think I can officially call you a {i}proper{/i} novice, now... But the road to fishing is long and arduous, so keep going... |f|ChangeImageLayer|/|Expression|/|1|/|ItsFine|n|...At least until you get bored. The fish aren't going anywhere, so don't be afraid to take a break and get back to it whenever you feel like it.",
                                                "2",  "|f|ChangeImageLayer|/|Expression|/|1|/|Happy|n|Oh, you didn't stop, huh? Hehe, you're already better than most of the slimes around here! Keep going and help out Sleim Vllge more while honing your fishing skills, beginner!",
                                                "1",  "|f|ChangeImageLayer|/|Expression|/|1|/|Smug|n|On your first fish still... The start of your fishing adventure. I'm sure you can catch plenty more... But for now, you're still a beginner. Show me your skills and you'll graduate to novice, hehe!",
                                              "EndLoop",
                                              "She then goes back to her own fishing, though you also notice her eyes zipping from one fisher to the next while her mouth occasionally silently moves in thought... Is she actually keeping a count of {i}all{/i} the fish people have caught?",
                                              "DisplayCharacters",
                                              "EndLoop",
                                              "JumpToScene", "FishingMenu"
                                        ]
                          },

